      <title>Netflix 称目前有 7000 万用户观看带有广告的节目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/netflix-says-70-million-users-now-watch-shows-with-advertising</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Netflix 公司表示，每月有 7000 万观众观看带有广告的节目，几乎是 5 月份总数的两倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/netflix-says-70-million-users-now-watch-shows-with-advertising</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
