    <item>
      <title>购物需求推动 Sea 股价上涨，利润上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/sea-tops-profit-estimates-after-fending-off-tiktok-lazada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在其电子商务业务报告其首次实现调整后盈利后，Sea 有限公司的股价出现了一年半多以来的最大涨幅，这表明该公司在印度尼西亚等东南亚市场上与规模更大的中国竞争对手保持着一定地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/sea-tops-profit-estimates-after-fending-off-tiktok-lazada</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 11:35:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国芯片制造商有望在 2025 年实现转机，英飞凌股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/infineon-expects-2025-revenue-decline-amid-weak-car-chip-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国芯片制造商英飞凌科技股份公司 (Infineon Technologies AG) 表示，预计到 2025 财年末业绩将出现好转，这意味着汽车需求的长期低迷状态可能即将结束。随后，该公司股价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/infineon-expects-2025-revenue-decline-amid-weak-car-chip-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 06:32:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
